{"tid":1012111,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)年初三節目","createTime":"2019-02-07T10:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T21:08:08.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75fe4e7c8855a42d0bcb3e76657b0e0d33a78c9b","tid":1012111,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=ed26d672\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=7b199beb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=16228076\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6f/Machete_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6f%2FMachete_poster.jpg&h=6753fbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/94/True_Lies.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F94%2FTrue_Lies.jpg&h=875f314e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9b/Machete_Kills_2013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9b%2FMachete_Kills_2013.jpg&h=0de9180c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1-2.<img src=\"https://img.itw01.com/images/2018/04/01/02/2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg!r1024x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itw01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F02%2F2413_uLvtC6_VZNSWED.jpg%21r1024x0.jpg&h=c1edbe40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.哈里（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾演）是一名隸屬於美國國家安全情報組織「奧米加局」（Omega Sector）的資深超級特工，精通多國語言並且擁有高技術性的間接手段。哈里及他的同伴們正接受了一個重要任務------調查1個名為「紅蓮聖戰」的恐怖主義組織所策劃的私運核彈頭並於美國發動襲擊的案件。任務期間他認識了「紅蓮聖戰」的重要幹部------表面為古玩商人的朱諾，並為了查緝需要而接近她<br />\n<br />\n4.故事圍繞墨西哥人科爾特斯（丹尼&middot;特喬）展開，講述他在墨西哥和自己的兄弟們拯救那些被綁架的女孩子們的故事。<br />\n<br />\n5.該片承接《絕煞刀鋒》故事，自從墨西哥人科爾特斯（丹尼&middot;特喬）幹掉德克薩斯州的黑幫之後，聲名日隆，被美國總統任命為特使，負責追殺一個卡特爾組織從墨西哥越過邊境來到美國的恐怖分子...<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=08f79b7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=becee1c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a240a9ae9602e4e989e5ea9bdb0f8f799a29aa06","tid":1012111,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"